=== RAW MODEL ANSWER ===
Answer: Step 1: Start from 3-bromo-5-hydroxyanisole and do Williamson O-alkylation with ethyl bromoacetate to give ethyl 2-(3-bromo-5-methoxyphenoxy)acetate | Step 2: In parallel, assemble the N-methylated imino-lactam heterocycle bearing the 2,4-dimethylphenyl substituent and convert its coupling site to the corresponding heteroaryl boronic acid/boronate | Step 3: Pd-catalyzed Suzuki coupling of ethyl 2-(3-bromo-5-methoxyphenoxy)acetate with the heteroaryl boronic acid/boronate to form ethyl 2-(3-(heteroaryl)-5-methoxyphenoxy)acetate | Step 4: Hydrolyze the ethyl ester to the free acid to furnish COc1cc(-c2cc(=Nc3c(C)cc(C)cc3C)n(C)c(=O)n2C)ccc1OCC(=O)O

